msgctxt "796"
msgid "Distraught Family Man"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72_Man Who is Hopelessly Single"
msgid "What's up? You're looking pretty glum."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84_Distraught Family Man"
msgid "Ya heard about that suicide this mornin'? I go past there on my way to work every day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96_Distraught Family Man"
msgid "There was a girl 'bout my daughter's age there lookin' completely distraught. Might've been the daughter of the lady who killed herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108_Distraught Family Man"
msgid "Couldn't bear to think of my girl havin' to go through somethin' like that."
msgstr ""

